{"tid":1346897,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣組注意] 7/28光復元朗應定名為「珍珠港行動」","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:10:13.000Z","uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"703b8ef9fd4fff349e4f64be071744f444d8478f","tid":1346897,"uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 7/7旺角、7/13上水、7/14沙田、7/21上環+元朗，呢幾日絕對稱得上係Days of Infamy。Day of Infamy (中譯「國恥日」或「恥辱之日」) 呢個term來自美國總統羅斯福喺1941年日本海軍空襲珍珠港後向國會發表演說並要求對日宣戰 (link: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infamy_Speech\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FInfamy_Speech&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIFR4K0ufT%2FFGu3kbIPb6xA8%3D&h=f5c6062c\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infamy_Speech</a>)<br />\n<br />\n2. 以前既香港絕對當得上Pearl of the Orient，而今日港共政權正無所不用其極將令香港成功既基礎一一摧毀 (言論自由、集會自由、免於恐懼的自由乜乜乜)。將行動代號定為「珍珠港」除咗紀念香港作為東方之珠既美好時光之外，亦都係帶出對未來既盼望。<br />\n<br />\n另外可考慮用呢幾個hashtag:<br />\n#光復香港<br />\n#時代革命<br />\n#LiberateHongKong<br />\n#RevolutionoftheTimes<br />\n#722YuenLong<br />\n#neverforget<br />\n#MenInWhite<br />\n#statesponsoredterrorism"},{"pid":"1af38453348c2b4e826ecf497a3cd42d9b698cb0","tid":1346897,"uid":184488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:02:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be4994a59e11fc5d6654f35172cd87f46d6bd50a","tid":1346897,"uid":38383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再推依個post 開過個727<br />\n唔好再推依個post 開過個727<br />\n唔好再推依個post 開過個727<br />\n唔好再推依個post 開過個727<br />\n唔好再推依個post 開過個727<br />\n唔好再推依個post 開過個727<br />\n唔好再推依個post 開過個727<br />\n唔好再推依個post 開過個727<br />\n唔好再推依個post 開過個727</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"424d9ed0c6f31b7d3ac6fb9794b14b3c01254fa6","tid":1346897,"uid":115982,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:03:45.000Z